MOTOR CONTROLLER 29  <-------->  ARDUINO
 ============================================= 
 WHITE (signal)           Digital pin 9
 RED (power)              VIN (Battery Power -- 5V works too, but won't be as strong or fast)
 BLACK (ground)           Ground (GND)                    

